                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                        <img src="~/Content/images/08.png" class="mb-1" alt="">飯局詳細地點： <input class="mb-1" type="text" name="f活動地點">
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                        <img src="~/Content/images/20.png" class="mb-1" alt="">團圖：<input class="mb-1"
