                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="modalContentRight">
                                                    <p>
                                                        <img src="~/Content/images/04.png" class="mb-1" alt="">預算：<input class="mb-1"
                                                                                                                         type="text" name="f活動預算">
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                        <img src="~/Content/images/17.png" class="mb-1" alt="">分類：<select name="f活動分類">
